1778:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****       (+) Configure timer remapping capabilities.
1779:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****       (+) Select timer input source.
